      <section class="- topic/section ">
         <title class="- topic/title ">Outer Control Loop Calibration</title>
         <p class="- topic/p ">
            <note class="- topic/note ">Schneider
Electric does not recommend calibrating the outer control loop. Instead
It is preferred to do the transformer calibration very precisely.</note>The following settings are used for the outer control loop. For one
phase system the Ph-N voltage x 10 must be entered. For three phase
systems the Ph-Ph voltage x 10 must be entered.<table outputclass="font:10" pgwide="1" class="- topic/table ">
