                     </row>
                  </thead>
                  <tbody class="- topic/tbody ">
                     <row class="- topic/row ">
                        <entry class="- topic/entry ">21</entry>
                        <entry class="- topic/entry ">Charger offset<fn class="- topic/fn ">100 means no offset</fn>
                        </entry>
                     </row>
                  </tbody>
               </tgroup>
            </table>If the charge current measured is higher than the displayed
current value the setting must also be lowered. A difference of 10
means approximately 0.7 A.</p>
